Program operation
=================

   The program is controlled via menus or corresponding short-cut keys
(where such exist, they are shown in the menus). Keypresses which are
not intercepted by the system or the graphical user interface are
interpreted by the ZX Spectrum keyboard emulation (see @{"Keyboard layout" Link "Keyboard layout"}).


 @{" The Project menu " Link "The Project menu"} 
 @{" The Settings menu " Link "The Settings menu"} 
 @{" The Emulation menu " Link "The Emulation menu"} 
 @{" The Processor menu " Link "The Processor menu"} 

